# Design export preview

When emitting or remapping `.fig` / `.sketch` for visual review:

- **Do** auto-open Sketch archives (`open …/*.sketch`)
- **Do not** auto-open Figma archives (`.fig` / `.deck`) — they are previewed in the browser
- Still write both formats when requested; only skip launching Figma
